WEBVTT

00:03:28.563 --> 00:03:30.129
that can survive without water.

00:03:30.371 --> 00:03:33.646
If we put water there, those will vanish.

00:03:33.858 --> 00:03:37.089
Stronger animals will come 
and destroy them.

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:40.708
Everything in nature has a meaning.

00:03:41.043 --> 00:03:43.069
Some meaning.

00:03:43.465 --> 00:03:48.475
Delhi, Chennai, Bangalore,
Mumbai, pick any city.

00:03:48.837 --> 00:03:51.947
More than 50 percent of its
water comes from jungles.

00:03:52.168 --> 00:03:55.087
Why don’t people understand that

00:03:55.402 --> 00:03:58.157
if we destroy our source of water,

00:03:58.379 --> 00:03:59.848
where will we get water from?